{"tid":1163210,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"「又柒一獲」鬼佬streamer Patrick Boivin，因為係Epic store買太多驚而被封鎖帳號！","createTime":"2019-05-20T10:06:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T17:29:58.000Z","uid":33359,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fad3ae8bb4bc3e4f5fc1356cf4f363b7c851729f","tid":1163210,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T10:06:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img2.tgbus.com/i/600_/cms3.0/2019/0520/20190520123812-3574-21504.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg2.tgbus.com%2Fi%2F600_%2Fcms3.0%2F2019%2F0520%2F20190520123812-3574-21504.jpg&h=0ce0a114&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img2.tgbus.com/i/600_/cms3.0/2019/0520/20190520123812-4539-10801.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg2.tgbus.com%2Fi%2F600_%2Fcms3.0%2F2019%2F0520%2F20190520123812-4539-10801.png&h=6767489d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nEpic官方人員Nick Chester對此做出回應，稱這是因為Boivin連續高頻率購買遊戲，遭到平台嚴厲反欺詐系統的警覺，賬號因此被鎖定.Nick Chester建議Boivin同客服部門聯繫並接受調查以解鎖賬號。<br />\n<br />\nBoivin對此十分不滿。因為自己之所以連續付款是因為史詩目前還沒有&ldquo;購物車&rdquo;功能，對多款遊戲感興趣的他不得不連續對遊戲單獨付款。他認為，Epic平台的功能不完善才應為誤判負責。"},{"pid":"3e5472e48a85f5527da0dfc5d4a51c1346583b02","tid":1163210,"uid":136186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T10:11:04.000Z","msg":"因為史詩目前還沒有&ldquo;購物車&rdquo;功能"},{"pid":"c978e85b8f4484fc8a8c1778558fce817d383857","tid":1163210,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e5472e48a85f5527da0dfc5d4a51c1346583b02","tid":1163210,"uid":136186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T10:11:04.000Z","msg":"因為史詩目前還沒有&ldquo;購物車&rdquo;功能"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T10:12:37.000Z","msg":"梳,本身篇文係殘體,掟入translate先貼上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20679853338c6ddea8ca58f2a61b6e64458140f3","tid":1163210,"uid":125479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T10:12:53.000Z","msg"